title: Reservist runs 74 miles in memory of fallen Airman (Dobbins Air Reserve Base)
text: ( Source : Dobbins Air Reserve Base ) BUCKLEY AIR FORCE BASE , Colo. -- In an effort to raise money for families of fallen Airmen, one reservist pushed herself to complete a 74-mile run around Lake Tahoe , Oct. 7-8. Maj. Jenny Poisson ,
